          <p>MMM is very good at judging brand type-awareness campaigns where you may not be event driven but it increases the bandwidth and the quality of other marketing activities. Traditional digital attribution almost always comes up short in valuing these upper-funnel activities because we don't have blanked tracking of conversions from something directly related to them. MMM, in other hand, uses statistical modeling to demonstrate how overall conversion rates increase when brand awareness campaigns are active.</p>
          
