          <p>Custom Neon's holistic strategy of multi-channel funnel optimization stands as an example of how intelligent coordination through every customer touch-point can create significant business expansion. Their holistic approach demonstrated proven successes at all levels of the user journey and vintage, focusing on employing structured optimization strategies.</p>
          
